Package: dol.gov
Title: Department of Labor Foreign Labor Disclosure Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Department of Labor foreign labor
    disclosure data. Covers PERM, H-1B, H-2A, H-2B, CW-1, and prevailing wage
    programs. Scrapes the DOL performance page for XLSX file links and downloads/
    parses them into tibbles. Includes LLM context injection via dol_context().
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: httr2, dplyr, tibble, xml2, readxl
NeedsCompilation: no
